{"tid":1427407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑因掩護示威者助逃走被控 踢拖夜間清潔工被控阻差辦公罪須宵禁","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:36:13.000Z","uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ebb9ea04c83148f13326dba85de8f41681a3fc4","tid":1427407,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190807/large/1565151982_45e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190807%2Flarge%2F1565151982_45e1.jpg&h=9e53d21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「8.5全港三罷」當天，多區有示威者堵路。一名居於深水埗的夜間清潔男工，疑因掩護在長沙灣堵路的示威者，好讓示威者逃走，被控阻差辦公罪。案件今在九龍城裁判法院提堂。裁判官將案件押後至10月2日再訊，其間批准被告以1,000元保釋外出，但須遵守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n被告何永隆（49歲）被指於本月5日在深水埗欽州街及長沙灣道交界阻礙執行公務的警長馮耀彤。被告為深水埗街坊，報稱居於鴨寮街。辯方指，被告事發時只穿著拖鞋，沒有戴頭盔、口罩或眼罩，警方拘捕他可能是誤中副車。據了解，辯方曾就宵禁令一事作出陳詞，指被告為夜更清潔工，每月開工24日，月入約15,000元，目前有經濟困難，連本月租金也難以繳交，不能失去工作；不過，裁判官仍決定頒下宵禁令，僅向辯方謂：「咁佢自己諗下。」<br />\n據悉，控方指事發時長沙灣政府合署附近有人群聚集堵路，警方在現場築起防線。當時有示威者表現激動，大聲叫喊。警長欲上前了解，被告突然從旁跑出，張開雙臂，用身體阻擋警長，並且大叫：「快啲走啦﹗快啲走啦！」該名示威者隨即離去，至今仍未被尋獲。<br />\n<br />\n案件暫時毋須答辯，等候警方進一步調查，控方並將向律政司就控罪及有關證據索取法律意見，其間不反對被告保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190807/59906388?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2x9AtztT-djRkpJpZ-2dGQgsukLdukMG4VHPkKVxXP6Wgo1OOqGKQ3f-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190807%2F59906388%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2x9AtztT-djRkpJpZ-2dGQgsukLdukMG4VHPkKVxXP6Wgo1OOqGKQ3f-Q&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75ZwEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=142d7468\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190807%2F59906388%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2x9AtztT-djRkpJpZ-2dGQgsukLdukMG4VHPkKVxXP6Wgo1OOqGKQ3f-Q&h=90c7e267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190807/59906388?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2x9AtztT-djRkpJpZ-2dGQgsukLdukMG4VHPkKVxXP6Wgo1OOqGKQ3f-Q</a>"},{"pid":"a539bb18ccc48caf5d31247c5a3dd2fe5c39b493","tid":1427407,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0169c35bfc7c086d256f32efeedfa15584986908","tid":1427407,"uid":128117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"清潔工就冇得用工作原因改保釋條件<br />\n係法庭上真係窮人含撚"},{"pid":"b4293c5f1d52354f4e607ad746df5ddd2e77e1a4","tid":1427407,"uid":170154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b4198d2e1c01efc37f744d635a10dab1988774","tid":1427407,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"當時有示威者表現激動，大聲叫喊。警長欲上前了解，被告突然從旁跑出，張開雙臂，用身體阻擋警長，並且大叫：「快啲走啦﹗快啲走啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f4f65d6c2c57d4e3f6f0514cff7491a35bceb2","tid":1427407,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:13:06.000Z","